#: ../../../release_details/9.4/legend-scale-actor.md:1
msgid "vtkLegendScaleActor improvements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/legend-scale-actor.md:3
msgid "vtkLegendScaleActor has been improved in several ways:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/legend-scale-actor.md:4
msgid "The axes appearance can be configured using a vtkProperty2D"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/legend-scale-actor.md:5
msgid ""
"In non-adjusted mode, the number of horizontal and vertical ticks can be "
"configured"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/legend-scale-actor.md:6
msgid ""
"Label values can be formatted using fixed-point or scientific notation in "
"addition to the default formatting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/legend-scale-actor.md:7
msgid ""
"`XY_COORDINATES` was replaced by a more generic `COORDINATES`, where main "
"axis is automatically found."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/legend-scale-actor.md:8
msgid ""
"In coordinates mode, an `Origin` can be set to shift the coordinates on each "
"axis."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/legend-scale-actor.md:9
msgid "The full grid can optionally be displayed"
msgstr ""
